OL,3,CWoman left feeling 'like terrorist'
OL,4,Cover airport treatment
OL,6,FBelfast international airport has been
OL,7,Fforced to apologise to a woman with a
OL,8,Fstoma who was not once but twice
OL,9,Fsearched as she went through security.
OL,11,FRhonda O'Neill told UTV her treatment
OL,12,Fwas deeply upsetting and humiliating
OL,13,Fsaying she felt "treated like a
OL,14,Fterrorist".
OL,16,FShe said the civil aviation authority
OL,17,Ftold her the proper procedures were
OL,18,Fnot followed despite the airport
OL,19,Finsisting to UTV that they were.
