OL,3,CWoman left feeling 'like terrorist'
OL,4,Cover airport treatment
OL,6,FThe 51-year-old from Desertmartin
OL,7,Foutside Magherafelt, who has a rare
OL,8,Fcondition known as autonomic
OL,9,Fneuropathy, was already anxious ahead
OL,10,Fof a hospital appointment in London to
OL,11,Fremove a hernia and reverse her stoma.
OL,13,FThen as she made her way through
OL,14,Fsecurity her stoma was flagged in the
OL,15,Fscanner.
OL,17,FDespite having a medical card to show
OL,18,Fher condition she says one worker
OL,19,Fasked her to lift her skirt to prove
OL,20,Fit and pressed on her abdomen which
OL,21,Fwas extremely painful.
