OL,3,CWoman left feeling 'like terrorist'
OL,4,Cover airport treatment
OL,6,FRhonda refused to reveal her stoma and
OL,7,Fwas taken to a private room with two
OL,8,Fwomen without her sister with whom she
OL,9,Fwas travelling. She claims no consent
OL,10,Fform was offered.
OL,12,F"To ask somebody to expose themselves,
OL,13,Ftheir bottom half alone, never mind
OL,14,Fthe stoma, it really is dreadful, "
OL,15,FRhonda said.
OL,17,F"It's hard enough travelling with this
OL,18,Fstoma and with an illness without
OL,19,Fbeing made to feel like you're a
OL,20,Fterrorist."
