OL,6,FWhen Rhonda was about to board her
OL,7,Fflight the airline refused to accept
OL,8,Fher driving licence as identification.
OL,9,FShe was forced to rebook with another
OL,10,Fcarrier and pay for a fresh flight by
OL,11,Fwhich time her stoma had burst.
OL,13,F"By this stage the tears were coming
OL,14,Fdown.I'm a strong lady but this was
OL,15,Fjust too much and I was pleading to
OL,16,Fthe security guards can you please get
OL,17,Fsomeone quick to help me?"
