OL,3,CWoman left feeling 'like terrorist'
OL,4,Cover airport treatment
OL,6,FGiven what she had endured just a
OL,7,Fcouple of hours earlier Rhonda thought
OL,8,Fshe would be waved through security
OL,9,Fbut instead she was forced to go
OL,10,Fthrough another search.
OL,12,F"I was marched with these two ladies
OL,13,Finto this wee room again and I said
OL,14,FI've been through this. I've already
OL,15,Fshown my stoma but they said you're
OL,16,Fgoing to have to show it again. I
OL,17,Fthought I'm not going to get on this
OL,18,Fplane unless I comply," she told us.
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@WO]
