OL,3,CWoman left feeling 'like terrorist'
OL,4,Cover airport treatment
OL,6,FWhen she finally got to clean her
OL,7,Fstoma it was in a disabled toilet
OL,8,Fwithout adequate facilities.
OL,10,F"Absolutely no facilities for people
OL,11,Fwith stomas. There are no benches or
OL,12,Fanything. I had to put my stoma
OL,13,Fsupplies on the toilet which is
OL,14,Funsanitary to change. That needs to be
OL,15,Faddressed as well," she added.
OL,17,FIn a response to Rhonda from the Civil
OL,18,FAviation Authority they said their
OL,19,Fguidance suggests ''no security
OL,20,Fofficer should need to touch a stoma
OL,21,Fbag or other medical device.''
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@SO]
