OL,3,CWoman left feeling 'like terrorist'
OL,4,Cover airport treatment
OL,6,FIt went on say "security officers
OL,7,Fshould be trained to be aware that
OL,8,Fpassengers may be carrying a stoma and
OL,9,Fto treat the passenger with
OL,10,Fappropriate sensitivity and discretion
OL,11,Fat all times and in a way that
OL,12,Frespects their privacy.''
OL,14,FIn a statement to UTV Belfast
OL,15,FInternational airport said it
OL,16,F''sincerely apologised'' to Rhonda but
OL,17,Finsisted they had followed ''all
OL,18,Frequired Civil Aviation Authority
OL,19,Fprocedures".
