OL,4,Cover airport treatment
OL,6,FIt went on to say: ''We are continuing
OL,7,Fto regularly review our procedures and
OL,8,Fenhance staff training around
OL,9,Fdisability awareness and security
OL,10,Fprocedures in relation to hidden and
OL,11,Fnon-mobility conditions, to ensure
OL,12,Fincidents such as this are handled
OL,13,Fappropriately in the future."
OL,15,FAt her home with her horses Rhonda is
OL,16,Fin her happy place.
OL,18,FBut her experience at security in
OL,19,FBelfast international airport left her
OL,20,Fdistressed and humiliated and now
OL,21,Fshe's angry.
